277
00:19:45,850 --> 00:19:46,840
Oh boy.

278
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:51,210
They have a fortune inside.

279
00:19:52,290 --> 00:19:53,670
Open it.

280
00:19:53,670 --> 00:19:55,500
This is yours.

281
00:20:01,340 --> 00:20:02,580
Let me see.

282
00:20:05,690 --> 00:20:08,150
This means you'll find what you're looking for.

283
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:13,220
I didn't know you'd be that happy.

284
00:20:25,910 --> 00:20:27,910
