289
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:06,280
Thank you.

290
00:21:10,490 --> 00:21:11,910
I hope not.

291
00:21:16,370 --> 00:21:19,380
I hope I'm smiling.

292
00:21:22,450 --> 00:21:23,590
What's wrong?

293
00:21:25,220 --> 00:21:26,610
You're still afraid...

294
00:21:27,370 --> 00:21:28,790
We're alone.

295
00:21:28,790 --> 00:21:30,600
There's no one there.

296
00:21:32,510 --> 00:21:34,950
Can you remember anything?

297
00:21:39,730 --> 00:21:42,470
You don't have to.

298
00:21:42,470 --> 00:21:43,930
I told you, didn't I?

299
00:21:43,930 --> 00:21:46,320
I don't need your past or future.

300
00:21:47,250 --> 00:21:48,860
Just stay as you are.

301
00:21:49,570 --> 00:21:51,630
We're in the eternity now. {In notes. -des}

302
00:21:55,750 --> 00:21:58,330
I love you, Selty.

303
00:22:15,360 --> 00:22:19,080
That night, after a long time,

304
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:22,270
