305
00:22:41,690 --> 00:22:43,270
I am here.

306
00:22:44,190 --> 00:22:45,780
Right here.

307
00:24:15,550 --> 00:24:17,430
My love is different.

308
00:24:17,430 --> 00:24:20,560
